channel.title: 508 GWD glitch
channel.description: In my 508 server that I'm making, when you go to godwars dungeon, sometimes you fall through the ground and d/c, and when you log back in you stay there. If anyone knows how to fix this please help, I have tried adding a command such as ::ground which teleports yourself to your coordinates on the server but it still doesnt work, so if anyone could actually help me to prevent falling thru the ground completely it would be great, thanks.
